my drawing mood is as fickle as a faerie but this picture of 80s peter parker made my fingers itch like its got it all the mullet the daisy dukes the crop top good god how could i not draw it???

so i’ll be drawing this bad boy swinging like modern day spidey-boo, but ive one trouble: what sort of shoes should he wear? i’m thinking some thotty thotty boots but i don’t know what kind please someone help me

summary:
Peter Parker (Spider-man)
I see all these post about Tony is Peters “dad” and how most people do these cute picture series,...
body:
Peter Parker (Spider-man)

I see all these post about Tony is Peters “dad” and how most people do these cute picture series, fanfics and small videos of them being father and son and it’s cute. I really miss Peter and yeah I love Tom Holland btw 💓

In infinity war my heart broke into pieces and it still are because every character I love (almost) just went to ashes when Thanos that bastard snapped his small fingers and wiped out half of the population on earth. That was cruel and what he did to the other planets? Damn… it’s sad.. what do you think about infinity war when that came out? Have you seen Endgame yet?

As always these gifs are my life and I love them very much when they especially are with my favorite characters. The love for Avengers are infinity ♾ Bless them all 💞 right?
